id: pm-45lr
title: 2026-07-15 full CLI SDK and ecosystem manual audit and optimization plan (review pass 91)
description: "Tracker-only manual audit of the complete pm CLI, public SDK, repository architecture, agent UX, performance, security, code quality, tests, docs, skills, bundled packages, installed packages, and all 18 active external pm package repositories. This plan records findings and sequencing only; no product implementation belongs in this session."
